 populace.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Mrz 2023) 0aMiraclesvFiction. 0aTelevision actors and actressesvInterviews. 0aTelevision producers and directorsvInterviews. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aKooreman, Thomas E., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Texas Press Complete eBook-Package Pre-2000z978311074535140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780292753624423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780292753624/original  a978-3-11-074535-1  University of Texas Press Complete eBook-Package Pre-2000b2000  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK